description:
I found TV footage of this song, stripped out the crappy sound & put the master stereo version in.
Astrud Gilberto (vocal), Antonio Carlos Jobim (guitar, vocal), Joao Donato (piano),  Joe Mondragon (bass),  Marty Paich (arranger, conductor). 
Recorded January 27 & 28, 1965
